item.title: CVE-2023-0094|2024-08-02T05:02:43.631Z -- unknown -- upqode%20google%20maps
item.description: The UpQode Google Maps WordPress plugin through 1.0.5 does not validate and escape some of its shortcode attributes before outputting them back in a page/post where the shortcode is embed, which could allow users with the contributor role and above to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attacks.
